definitions.definition: Of a geologic period within the Cenozoic era ; comprises the Miocene , Pliocene , Pleistocene and Holocene epochs from about 26 million years ago to the present.

main_definition: ( geology ) Of a geologic period within the Cenozoic era ; comprises the Miocene , Pliocene , Pleistocene and Holocene epochs from about 26 million years ago to the present.
